ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition1
ScalarVariable.description: eSAC1A.simpleLagLim.state < eSAC1A.simpleLagLim.outMin and eSAC1A.simpleLagLim.K * eSAC1A.imLeadLag.y - eSAC1A.simpleLagLim.state > 0.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition2
ScalarVariable.description: eSAC1A.simpleLagLim.state > eSAC1A.simpleLagLim.outMax and eSAC1A.simpleLagLim.K * eSAC1A.imLeadLag.y - eSAC1A.simpleLagLim.state < 0.0
